## Efficiency Issues in Git Diff

### Issue 1: Unnecessary Manual Loops → Set Constructor (Claude Section, line 386-391)

**Type:** Unnecessary loop - can be replaced with Set constructor

**Location:** `src/index.ts`, lines 386-391 (Claude section)

